    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a bit sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is an absolute gem\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one and it still looks and drives like it just rolled off the lot! No scratches, no smells, just pure perfection. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the dealership price tag, you\u2019ve found it. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44500.0,
